00:19:55.440 --> 00:19:55.800
Okay.

00:20:00.240 --> 00:20:01.040
Alright, let's try some on, too.

00:20:03.660 --> 00:20:04.260
Right this way, please.

00:20:17.880 --> 00:20:18.540
This one's good.

