I'd recommend snowboarding.

00:20:37.240 --> 00:20:38.300
Guys look so cool doing it.

00:20:40.060 --> 00:20:40.600
I can give it a try.

00:20:41.360 --> 00:20:42.300
Yeah, try it out.

